  "industry_note": "UNS N07718 / EN 2.4668 / AMS 5662 / GH4169 / NC19FeNb — Ni-base γ'' precipitation-hardened superalloy (Ni 50-55, Cr 17-21, Fe bal, Nb 4.75-5.5, Mo 2.8-3.3, Ti 0.65-1.15, Al 0.2-0.8). Service temp 650°C (γ'' decomposes >680°C). AM LPBF 의 가장 흔한 superalloy — turbine disks, combustor liners, rocket engine thrust chambers, oil/gas wellhead.",
